    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >一场暴力与美交织的银河恶魔城之旅</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >发现新的路线，为杰克获取强大的升级，一边与新巴塞罗那的黑帮和犯罪头目斗争，一边调整你的游戏风格。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119940/extras/fcbb2a3a1e910c60ead6dd9cdcb15a40.poster.avif?t=1771588216\" width=1170 height=656 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119940/extras/fcbb2a3a1e910c60ead6dd9cdcb15a40.webm?t=1771588216\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119940/extras/fcbb2a3a1e910c60ead6dd9cdcb15a40.mp4?t=1771588216\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >飞船、船长和船员 </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >改装希望号——杰克的宇宙飞船和行动基地。升级希望号，招募新的船员，把它打造成你自己的飞船。你的选择将直接影响杰克的能力和游戏风格。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119940/extras/b3b9d2d6082e44d39b7f2d729a5e168e.poster.avif?t=1771588216\" width=1170 height=656 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119940/extras/b3b9d2d6082e44d39b7f2d729a5e168e.webm?t=1771588216\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119940/extras/b3b9d2d6082e44d39b7f2d729a5e168e.mp4?t=1771588216\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >建立人脉</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与丰富多彩的人物建立关系：重新联络杰克的老朋友，并结交新朋友！招募他们加入你的事业，建立人脉，甚至有可能在这个无情的世界中找到爱情。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119940/extras/c71621e850fcac0e40c372cdc0826a18.poster.avif?t=1771588216\" width=1170 height=656 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119940/extras/c71621e850fcac0e40c372cdc0826a18.webm?t=1771588216\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119940/extras/c71621e850fcac0e40c372cdc0826a18.mp4?t=1771588216\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >参与激烈的战斗</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >掌握快速、时尚的战斗系统，利用机动性、技能和强大的能力来克服敌人的无情攻击。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119940/extras/2653853d03855c5fe4f89c0cd0903c64.poster.avif?t=1771588216\" width=1170 height=656 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119940/extras/2653853d03855c5fe4f89c0cd0903c64.webm?t=1771588216\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119940/extras/2653853d03855c5fe4f89c0cd0903c64.mp4?t=1771588216\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >丰富多彩的敌人</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >遇到许多独特的敌人——从巨型蜥蜴团伙到机械人军队……别忘了还有众多凶恶的头目等着杰克去打败！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119940/extras/7c4c81ba012b251ae52b8826c33a1d4b.poster.avif?t=1771588216\" width=1170 height=656 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119940/extras/7c4c81ba012b251ae52b8826c33a1d4b.webm?t=1771588216\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119940/extras/7c4c81ba012b251ae52b8826c33a1d4b.mp4?t=1771588216\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >全明星编剧团队</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >该游戏的编剧是业界传奇人物Antony Johnston（《生化危机：村庄》、《死亡空间》）和Emma Beeby（《Still Wakes the Deep》、《Tails of Iron》）。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119940/extras/43ff966423680c002865ed3922d036b8.poster.avif?t=1771588216\" width=1170 height=656 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119940/extras/43ff966423680c002865ed3922d036b8.webm?t=1771588216\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119940/extras/43ff966423680c002865ed3922d036b8.mp4?t=1771588216\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >对巴塞罗那形象的重塑</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索新巴塞罗那，一个基于真实地点的未来城市！它拥有著名的地标建筑：圣母院、桂尔公园和其他许多景点！不过，它们看起来可能不是你期望的那样……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119940/extras/54ef6dfb9b0807627e93955e97db8471.poster.avif?t=1771588216\" width=1170 height=656 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119940/extras/54ef6dfb9b0807627e93955e97db8471.webm?t=1771588216\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119940/extras/54ef6dfb9b0807627e93955e97db8471.mp4?t=1771588216\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
